title._content: Window display for "Strike up the Band" (taken for M.G.M.), c.1941, by Sam Hood

tag.raw: State Library of New South Wales
tag.author: 29454428@N08

description._content: Notes: This musical film was released in the US in 1940 and starred Judy Garland and Mickey Rooney. The State Library's photographic collection contains many photographs of shop window displays featuring film tie-in advertising. Format: Photograph Find out more about this photograph: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/item/itemDetailPaged.aspx?itemID=12827 Search for more great images in the State Library's collections: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/search/SimpleSearch.aspx From the collection of the State Library of New South Wales: www.sl.nsw.gov.au
